Package: smash
Type: Package
Title: Smoothing using Adaptive SHrinkage (SMASH)
Version: 1.0
Date: 2015-01-26
Author: Matthew Stephens, Zhengrong Xing
Maintainer: Matthew Stephens <mstephens@uchicago.edu>
Description: Smash performs univariate signal denoising/nonparametric
    regression for Poisson distributed data or Gaussian distributed data with
    possibly heteroskedastic error terms.
License: GPL-3
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.1),
    Rcpp (>= 0.11.1),
    ashr,
    wavethresh,
    Matrix,
    data.table,
    caTools
LinkingTo: Rcpp
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Suggests:
    knitr
